---
import { Card } from '@/components/ui/card';
---

<section id="precos" class="py-20 bg-zinc-50/50 dark:bg-surface-darkSecondary/30 border-t border-zinc-200/50 dark:border-zinc-800/80 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-16">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold text-aura-600 dark:text-aura-400 uppercase tracking-widest bg-aura-50 dark:bg-aura-900/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Investimento Retornado</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
        Planos simples que crescem com a sua assessoria.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Comece com o plano ideal para a sua estrutura e escale a sua receita. Sem contratos rígidos de fidelidade.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Price Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Plan 1: Solo Planner -->
      <Card className="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-surface-darkSecondary flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] btn-transition shadow-soft text-left">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">Solo Planner</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">R$ 149<span class="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-normal">/mês</span></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Ideal para cerimonialistas independentes que organizam até 3 casamentos activos simultaneamente.
          </p>
          <hr class="border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800" />
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Até 3 casamentos ativos</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Painel financeiro de faturas</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Calendário de compromissos</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Relatórios básicos de faturamento</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🔴 Templates de casamentos</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://app.simaceito.site/register"
          class="w-full mt-8 py-3 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 font-bold rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider btn-transition text-center hover:bg-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-700"
        >
          Testar Gratuitamente
        </a>
      </Card>

      <!-- Plan 2: Agency Premium (Popular/Destacado) -->
      <Card style={{ overflow: 'visible' }} className="overflow-visible p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-aura-500 bg-white dark:bg-surface-darkSecondary flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] btn-transition shadow-glow relative text-left">
        <span class="absolute top-0 right-1/2 translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-aura-600 text-white font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest whitespace-nowrap">Mais Popular</span>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-aura-600 dark:text-aura-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">Agency Premium</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">R$ 299<span class="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-normal">/mês</span></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            A solução completa para pequenas e médias agências gerenciarem múltiplos noivos com controle absoluto.
          </p>
          <hr class="border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800" />
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Casamentos ativos ilimitados</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Templates de casamentos praia/campo</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Exportação de PDF para os Noivos</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Faturamento e parcelas ilimitadas</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Suporte prioritário 24/7</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://app.simaceito.site/register"
          class="w-full mt-8 py-3 bg-aura-600 hover:bg-aura-700 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider btn-transition shadow-md shadow-aura-500/25 text-center"
        >
          Testar Gratuitamente
        </a>
      </Card>

      <!-- Plan 3: Enterprise -->
      <Card className="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-surface-darkSecondary flex flex-col justify-between hover:scale-[1.02] btn-transition shadow-soft text-left">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">Enterprise</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">Sob Consulta</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Para grandes assessorias nacionais que necessitam de integrações ad-hoc e faturamento avançado.
          </p>
          <hr class="border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800" />
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Múltiplas agências regionais</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Controle de acessos da equipe</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 SLA e suporte de engenharia</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">🟢 Exportações customizadas adicionais</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a
          href="mailto:suporte@simaceito.site?subject=Interesse%20no%20Plano%20Enterprise"
          class="w-full mt-8 py-3 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 font-bold rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider btn-transition text-center hover:bg-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-700"
        >
          Falar com Consultor
        </a>
      </Card>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
